# Anderson County Focus Mode Build Plan

**Public county/city, working-landscape, trail, and history context — not property-title, zoning/legal, emergency, live-safety, infrastructure-vulnerability, or exact sensitive-location guidance.**

**Product thesis:** Build a public-safe Anderson County Focus Mode that lets users explore county/city government anchors, Garnett civic context, working-landscape aggregates, public recreation candidates, transportation context, and historical orientation only through governed, citation-backed, policy-filtered evidence surfaces.

