| “What official county source should I start with?” | Show Anderson County official-source card, source role, checked date, and allowed claim scope. | Explain that public web content is not legal reliance; redirect to official records when needed. |
| “What does Garnett’s official site cover?” | Show municipal categories and contact/source link. | No legal/zoning/compliance determination. |
| “What public services are visible for the county?” | Summarize department/service categories from admitted county source. | Do not produce emergency instructions, law-enforcement operations, or property title/access conclusions. |
| “What later layers could this county support?” | Show candidate source roadmap for Census, NASS, KDWP, KDOT, KSHS, FEMA/KDA/KGS. | Mark every non-admitted source `NEEDS_VERIFICATION`. |
| “Why won’t KFM answer my property/access question?” | Return denial panel with reason code and official-authority redirect. | Boundary is visible, not hidden. |

