| Policy denial | A parcel/title/access request returns `DENY` with `PROPERTY_TITLE_ACCESS_DENIED`. |
| Currentness failure | Trail/facility status request returns `ABSTAIN` unless a current official notice is admitted. |
| Source-role separation | County web, city web, KSHS history, NASS statistics, and FEMA maps are displayed as different source roles. |

